{"tid":796213,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GFRIEND信飛跳舞「手當場脫臼」　痛苦皺眉…敬業撐整首","createTime":"2018-08-27T15:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T11:02:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":104,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"15298910f36b5d1e5ddaf4840237a8a263d88f52","tid":796213,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"南韓女團GFRIEND以「刀群舞」聞名，她們對舞蹈整齊度要求嚴格、不斷追求進步，每每推出新曲的舞蹈都是越來越難，然而，信飛（SinB）過去曾因練舞過度造成左手慣性脫臼，她26日隨著團體舉辦演唱會，又被發現舊傷復發，表演到一半時，信飛忽然忍痛皺眉頭，但她敬業地完成整場演出，被粉絲看在眼裡相當心疼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3515/d3515921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3515%2Fd3515921.jpg&h=476a653e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND信飛表演到一半手脫臼。（圖／翻攝自saya2158やっさん/さやYoutube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGFRIEND於26日在馬尼拉舉辦「2018 Season of GFRIEND」演唱會，6人唱到夯歌《LOVE WHISPER》時，舞蹈瑣碎又複雜，且不少抬手、踢腿以及轉身的動作都很激烈，就在演出進行一半時，信飛的手臂慣性脫節舊傷復發，她雖隱約皺眉頭面露不適感，但一一消化，臉上笑容也不曾消失過，把左手放在身後敬業地完成舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3515/d3515918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3515%2Fd3515918.jpg&h=61a842d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND信飛結束還帶著笑容。（圖／翻攝自saya2158やっさん/さやYoutube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上，信飛2年前也曾在音樂節目表演上突然手脫臼，她同樣硬撐著完成舞台，馬尼拉演唱會表演片段的影片公開後，歌迷留言關心「舞蹈那麼激烈撐完整首不簡單」，也有粉絲擔心她的手臂狀況惡化，希望公司能儘早安排治療。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2jdHPMQeWXQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2jdHPMQeWXQ&d=W4EWNGLU8kWabEt6zhMsOZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=903029d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2jdHPMQeWXQ</a><br />\n<br />\nCLS甩住黎跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca02186b9bac4958c3ff712d7ed36f723854b12","tid":796213,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9889241dbff833e1d8db21058058c8b5ec282113","tid":796213,"uid":32577,"like":99,"dislike":21,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/233936_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F233936_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=3d7d41b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"040979fdc89d52f9cca64a44aac265cd1d34f962","tid":796213,"uid":32577,"like":71,"dislike":18,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/234017_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F234017_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=88af3c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2853cc43f52182d9db2795c321b4f428fd6c22a2","tid":796213,"uid":23021,"like":82,"dislike":13,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/be09f79d4130c0e6db33f4f4a46b1c30/tenor.gif?itemid=5049553\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fbe09f79d4130c0e6db33f4f4a46b1c30%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D5049553&h=12ca0b8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f5651c0a7212495f701ed598bbae3dbf9dd0795","tid":796213,"uid":99700,"like":53,"dislike":7,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170518/photo/bkn-20170518230023809-0518_00862_001_03p.jpg?20170518223735\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170518%2Fpho